msgstr ""

#: 18_best_friends_of_all_time.html:111
msgid "Hebrews 12:14-15"
msgstr ""

#: 18_best_friends_of_all_time.html:114
msgid "Be holy and prevent \"bad attitudes\" in one another"
msgstr ""

#: 18_best_friends_of_all_time.html:119
msgid "1 Thessalonians 5:12-14"
msgstr ""

#: 18_best_friends_of_all_time.html:122
msgid "Outlook toward one another"
msgstr ""

#: 18_best_friends_of_all_time.html:127
msgid "John 17:20-23"
msgstr ""

#: 18_best_friends_of_all_time.html:130
msgid "The ultimate goal of love and unity — world evangelism!"
msgstr ""

#: 18_best_friends_of_all_time.html:136
msgid "Date and marry only disciples"
msgstr ""

#: 18_best_friends_of_all_time.html:142
msgid "1 Corinthians 7:39"
msgstr ""

#: 18_best_friends_of_all_time.html:145
msgid "Marriage must only be in the Lord"
msgstr ""

#: 18_best_friends_of_all_time.html:150
msgid "2 Corinthians 6:14-7:1"
msgstr ""

#: 18_best_friends_of_all_time.html:153
msgid "Dating, as in marriage, is a partnership in which you are \"yoked together.\"  Disciples must separate from unbelievers to receive the promises of God"
msgstr ""

#: 18_best_friends_of_all_time.html:158
msgid "1 Kings 11:1-10"
msgstr ""

#: 18_best_friends_of_all_time.html:162
msgid "Nehemiah 13:23-27"
msgstr ""

#: 18_best_friends_of_all_time.html:165
